lib/
lib64/
# The Databricks-App export template ships a real frontend source dir named
# `lib/` (shadcn utils, markdown renderer, deck themes). It is NOT a Python venv
# lib — keep it tracked despite the `lib/` rule above, else exports break on a
# fresh clone (the files exist locally but never get committed).
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/lib/
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/lib/**
parts/
sdist/
var/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

